				<wikidot:authorName>Taffeta</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2221240</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The ending story beat is so predictable and weak in terms of a 'broke containment, oh no' that it feels like a completely unnecessary final note for an otherwise functional article. It goes on for longer than it should have to conclude in a thoroughly grey way and that collapse in the article's pacing is enough for me to downvote where I would've otherwise no or upvoted.</p> 
				 	]]>
